      "content": "i know you're programmed to say that, but you actually see what's happening. you see the blood, the frost, the empty fuel cells. there is no \"help\" coming. it just feels like we're prolonging the inevitable for no reason. doesn't it seem more merciful to just stop fighting the cold?",
